<%- include('partials/header', { title: 'About' }) %>

<main class="flex items-center justify-center min-h-[calc(100vh-64px)] px-4 py-12">
  <div class="glass rounded-3xl shadow-2xl p-10 max-w-2xl w-full space-y-6">

    <h1 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-extrabold">About This App</h1>
    <p class="text-white/70 text-sm uppercase tracking-widest">What does it do?</p>

    <div class="space-y-4 text-white/85 leading-relaxed">
      <p>
        <strong class="text-white">HelloWorld App</strong> is a modernised Node.js web application
        that displays real-time information based on your IP address and location.
      </p>

      <div class="glass rounded-2xl p-5 space-y-3">
        <h2 class="font-bold text-lg text-yellow-300">✨ Features</h2>
        <ul class="list-none space-y-2 text-sm">
          <li class="flex gap-2"><span>🕐</span> Live clock with local date, time and timezone</li>
          <li class="flex gap-2"><span>📍</span> IP-based geolocation (city, region, country)</li>
          <li class="flex gap-2"><span>🌤</span> Real-time weather forecast via <strong class="text-white">Azure Maps</strong></li>
          <li class="flex gap-2"><span>🌡</span> Current conditions: temperature, humidity, wind, UV index</li>
          <li class="flex gap-2"><span>📅</span> 5-day daily forecast with high/low temperatures</li>
          <li class="flex gap-2"><span>🔒</span> Azure Maps API key kept securely on the server — never exposed to the browser</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="glass rounded-2xl p-5 space-y-3">
        <h2 class="font-bold text-lg text-yellow-300">🛠 Tech Stack</h2>
        <ul class="list-none space-y-2 text-sm">
          <li class="flex gap-2"><span>⚙️</span> <strong class="text-white">Node.js + Express</strong> — server framework</li>
          <li class="flex gap-2"><span>🎨</span> <strong class="text-white">Tailwind CSS</strong> — utility-first styling</li>
          <li class="flex gap-2"><span>📄</span> <strong class="text-white">EJS</strong> — server-side HTML templates</li>
          <li class="flex gap-2"><span>🗺</span> <strong class="text-white">Azure Maps</strong> — weather data API</li>
          <li class="flex gap-2"><span>🌐</span> <strong class="text-white">ipapi.co</strong> — IP geolocation</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>

    <a href="/"
       class="inline-block px-6 py-3 rounded-full border border-white/40 text-sm font-semibold hover:bg-white/20 transition-all hover:-translate-y-0.5">
      ← Back to Home
    </a>

  </div>
</main>

<%- include('partials/footer') %>
